3108.description: The romantic encounter of strawberry and the sunny scent of orange come together for an ecstatic dessert time.

4002.name: Reed Flowers

4009.name: Dried Persimmon

4010.description: A soup made with highly fragrant and rich matsutake and chicken that have been slowly simmered together. It's warming and nutritious.

4011.name: Autumn Bouquet

4012.name: Peanut Oil

4013.name: Carrot and Pear Juice

110005.name: Berry Drink

110006.name: Grape Drink
